-Here you go.
-Appreciate you.

124
00:06:20.839 --> 00:06:22.757
My mammal. Finally. bro.

125
00:06:22.841 --> 00:06:24.801
Chill. Daryl. You ordered a water.

126
00:06:24.885 --> 00:06:26.887
Water is food too. bro.

127
00:06:26.970 --> 00:06:28.221
So. Hannah. how's Jett doing?

128
00:06:28.305 --> 00:06:30.432
