143
00:07:00.420 --> 00:07:02.297
Yeah. that was so not cool.

144
00:07:03.256 --> 00:07:05.759
All right. I'm out.
I'm gonna go train at the Cage.

145
00:07:05.842 --> 00:07:08.219
What? You're not gonna
watch the game with us?

146
00:07:08.303 --> 00:07:10.513
Nah. I gotta go while the Cage is empty.

147
00:07:10.597 --> 00:07:12.766
"cause after the game.
you know it's gonna fill up.

148
00:07:12.849 --> 00:07:15.435
Do not let Grizz catch you.

149
00:07:15.518 --> 00:07:16.519
I won't.

150
00:07:17.228 --> 00:07:20.440
Roots run deep. Roots run deep.

151
00:07:20.523 --> 00:07:21.775
Roots run deep.

152
00:07:37.874 --> 00:07:39.250
Step back. Jett!

153
00:07:41.044 --> 00:07:43.505
The crowd goes wild.

154
00:08:06.111 --> 00:08:07.112
Another one.

155
00:08:08.571 --> 00:08:11.700
With only five seconds left.
the ball goes to Harris.

156
00:08:11.783 --> 00:08:13.159
He's all alone.

157
00:08:13.243 --> 00:08:15.954
Three. two. one...

158
00:08:22.127 --> 00:08:23.712
What's going on here. folks?

159
00:08:23.795 --> 00:08:25.088
They're resetting the clock?

160
00:08:25.171 --> 00:08:26.297
Don't question it.

161
00:08:26.381 --> 00:08:28.258
He's got time for one more shot.

162
00:08:28.341 --> 00:08:30.844
Three. two. one...

163
00:08:39.227 --> 00:08:43.481
Roots run deep. Roots run deep.
Roots run deep.

164
00:08:43.565 --> 00:08:44.899
Roots run deep.

165
00:08:44.983 --> 00:08:47.318
One day. baby. One day.

166
00:08:54.451 --> 00:08:56.327
Get that weak sauce up out of here.

167
00:08:56.411 --> 00:08:58.621
Yo. what's your problem. Grizz?

168
00:08:58.705 --> 00:09:00.582
Every day you're here.

169
00:09:00.665 --> 00:09:03.084
Every day I gotta kick you out.

170
00:09:03.168 --> 00:09:05.003
I mean. what are the rules. y'all?

171
00:09:05.086 --> 00:09:07.088
Smalls can't ball.

172
00:09:07.172 --> 00:09:09.549
First off. I'm not a small. I'm a medium.

173
00:09:09.632 --> 00:09:11.593
What? Medium fries?

174
00:09:11.676 --> 00:09:14.137
You will never make it into Roar.

175
00:09:14.220 --> 00:09:16.181
I mean. come on. Let me run.

176
00:09:16.264 --> 00:09:18.141
I'm better than half of y'all anyways.

177
00:09:18.224 --> 00:09:19.768
Let me show you what I got.

178
00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:21.561
Ball me.

179
00:09:22.062 --> 00:09:24.731
Only thing you're running
is off this court.

180
00:09:25.899 --> 00:09:27.358
Now get out of here.

181
00:09:27.984 --> 00:09:28.985
Whatever.

182
00:09:29.069 --> 00:09:31.446
Good night. Shirley.
You're in my house now.

183
00:09:33.114 --> 00:09:35.825
And that's the game. Thorns lose by 26.

184
00:09:35.909 --> 00:09:37.577
Clock's ticking. Jett.

185
00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:40.872
Jett. Jett. Jett.
hey. can you sign this for me?

186
00:09:40.955 --> 00:09:43.833
Of course. Anything for a fan.

187
00:09:43.917 --> 00:09:44.918
There you go. kid.

188
00:09:45.001 --> 00:09:46.294
Thanks. Jett.

189
00:09:47.045 --> 00:09:48.713
Why can't you win a championship?

190
00:09:49.631 --> 00:09:51.091
Retire already!

191
00:09:51.174 --> 00:09:52.342
Jett. could we take a photo?

192
00:09:52.425 --> 00:09:53.843
Jett. third loss in a row.

193
00:09:53.927 --> 00:09:55.887
-How does it feel?
-Flo? Where's Flo?

194
00:09:55.970 --> 00:09:57.472
-When are we gonna stop sucking?
-Flo!

195
00:09:57.555 --> 00:09:58.848
Hey. Flo?

196
00:09:58.932 --> 00:10:00.100
Who's seen Flo?

197
00:10:12.112 --> 00:10:13.947
Hey. there. grumpy cat.

198
00:10:16.825 --> 00:10:18.743
How'd the game end?

199
00:10:18.827 --> 00:10:22.539
I stopped watching and punched myself
in the face instead.

200
00:10:23.081 --> 00:10:24.916
You think this is funny?

201
00:10:24.999 --> 00:10:26.876
You're the team owner. Flo.

202
00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.461
How am I supposed to win

203
00:10:28.545 --> 00:10:31.631
