by head cases and has-beens?

204
00:10:31.714 --> 00:10:33.258
Hey. I'm working on it.

205
00:10:33.341 --> 00:10:36.177
We don't even have a sixth player. Flo.
but you got your hooves done.

206
00:10:36.261 --> 00:10:40.181
Listen here. Jett.
free agents aren't free. Okay?

207
00:10:40.265 --> 00:10:42.767
So unless you have a sixth player in mind

208
00:10:42.851 --> 00:10:46.563
who can fill an arena
and doesn't want a big. fat check.

209
00:10:46.646 --> 00:10:49.566
I'm gonna get back to my mud bath. okay?

210
00:10:49.649 --> 00:10:51.192
That is hogwash.

211
00:10:51.276 --> 00:10:53.111
It's your job to figure it out.

212
00:10:53.194 --> 00:10:54.571
Trade players. sell the team...

213
00:10:54.654 --> 00:10:58.449
I don't care what you got to do.
Just do it. Now.

214
00:10:58.533 --> 00:11:01.619
Careful what you wish for. Jett.

215
00:11:06.958 --> 00:11:08.001
He's fine.

216
00:11:25.393 --> 00:11:28.313
Hey. I'm driving here.
Get out of the road. you medium.

217
00:11:28.396 --> 00:11:30.190
Keep it down. Why are you so loud?

218
00:11:33.776 --> 00:11:35.737
Hello. William.

219
00:11:35.820 --> 00:11:37.655
Hey. Frank. How are you?

220
00:11:37.739 --> 00:11:41.201
Would you happen to have that rent?

221
00:11:41.784 --> 00:11:43.828
Yeah. yeah. Right. Right.

222
00:11:43.912 --> 00:11:46.164
Frank. I got you. It's all right here.

223
00:11:46.247 --> 00:11:48.666
-I meant to give it to you today actually.
-22. 23...

224
00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:51.794
This is not actual money.
this piece of paper.

225
00:11:51.878 --> 00:11:53.004
Yeah. yeah. yeah. yeah.

226
00:11:53.087 --> 00:11:55.340
What about last month's
and the month before?

227
00:11:55.423 --> 00:11:58.384
Frank. it's me. Come on.

228
00:11:58.468 --> 00:12:01.429
I just need a little more time.

229
00:12:01.512 --> 00:12:03.640
You had time. Will.

230
00:12:04.349 --> 00:12:06.017
I got mouths to feed.

231
00:12:06.100 --> 00:12:07.852
I don't need one more.

232
00:12:07.936 --> 00:12:08.853
-Hey. Will.
-Hey. Will.

233
00:12:08.937 --> 00:12:10.396
-Hey. Will.
-Hey. Will.

234
00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:13.107
-Hey. guys.
-Hey. Will. Hey. Will.

235
00:12:13.191 --> 00:12:15.151
<i>Hey. Will. Hey. Will. Hey. Will.</i>

236
00:12:15.235 --> 00:12:16.236
Y'all are still awake?

237
00:12:16.319 --> 00:12:18.112
-Hey. Will.
-What's up. Theo?

238
00:12:18.196 --> 00:12:19.906
Did they let you play at the Cage today?

239
00:12:19.989 --> 00:12:21.491
You know me. I'm working on it.

240
00:12:21.574 --> 00:12:22.700
That's a lot of kids.

241
00:12:22.784 --> 00:12:24.202
Indeed it is.

242
00:12:24.285 --> 00:12:25.536
I'm sorry. kiddo.

243
00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:28.414
Look. get me my rent money by tomorrow

244
00:12:28.498 --> 00:12:30.875
or I gotta rent the room to somebody else.

245
00:12:30.959 --> 00:12:32.126
Capisce?

246
00:12:32.210 --> 00:12:34.462
-Will. I forgot to tell you--
-Hey. kids. come on. Get in the tub.

247
00:12:34.545 --> 00:12:35.546
Here we go. here we go.

248
00:12:43.721 --> 00:12:44.722
Whatever.

249
00:12:46.557 --> 00:12:47.558
You need money?

250
00:12:47.642 --> 00:12:51.312
Well. you're in luck 'cause you can start
earning up to 300 bucks per day.

251
00:12:51.396 --> 00:12:55.775
How? By trading crypto
on BigBroncoCrypto...

252
00:12:56.276 --> 00:12:59.237
Frank. I'm pregnant again.

253
00:12:59.320 --> 00:13:02.073
That's amazing. sweetheart.

254
00:13:03.074 --> 00:13:06.119
You know. we needed another one of those.

255
00:13:06.661 --> 00:13:07.704
Hey. Will.

256
00:13:08.204 --> 00:13:10.123
gonna need that rent money.

257
00:13:34.605 --> 00:13:37.025
Boom! Check these out.

258
00:13:37.108 --> 00:13:40.320
Vineland green. Fillmore Fours.
in the flesh.

259
00:13:40.403 --> 00:13:42.405
Jett wore these in the Furball game.

260
00:13:42.488 --> 00:13:44.657
