But you're broke.

266
00:13:54.751 --> 00:13:57.462
But if I had the Fours I wouldn't look it.

267
00:13:57.545 --> 00:14:00.131
Yes. Yes. you would. It's gonna be okay.

268
00:14:00.214 --> 00:14:03.176
Pristine upper mesh. Taut laces.

269
00:14:04.927 --> 00:14:06.763
-Nutty.
-Nasty.

270
00:14:06.846 --> 00:14:07.764
250.

271
00:14:07.847 --> 00:14:09.849
-Come on.
-2507 How dare you.

272
00:14:09.932 --> 00:14:11.559
The disrespect.

273
00:14:11.642 --> 00:14:13.936
Come on. Will. I can do installments.

274
00:14:14.020 --> 00:14:17.148
Yeah. yeah. that's great. Daryl.
but my landlord can't.

275
00:14:17.774 --> 00:14:18.900
Okay.

276
00:14:18.983 --> 00:14:20.902
I can't watch this.

277
00:14:20.985 --> 00:14:23.071
So. 4007

278
00:14:23.613 --> 00:14:25.031
-240.
-It's going down?

279
00:14:25.114 --> 00:14:27.617
-230.
-Dang. stop! Please. please!

280
00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:30.536
-Yo! Y'all are not gonna believe this.
-No way!

281
00:14:30.620 --> 00:14:34.874
Mane is at the Cage.
and he's taking on all challengers.

282
00:14:36.751 --> 00:14:40.963
