this is the best Vineland's got?

300
00:15:42.733 --> 00:15:45.403
I thought the Cage
is where roarball was born.

301
00:15:45.945 --> 00:15:50.575
I guess this town's only as weak
as its greatest player.

302
00:15:50.658 --> 00:15:52.243
Hey. where she at?

303
00:15:52.326 --> 00:15:56.998
If Jett's nowhere to be found.
then somebody gotta answer me.

304
00:15:57.081 --> 00:15:59.041
-Who's got next?
-I got next.

305
00:15:59.125 --> 00:16:00.334
Who said that?

306
00:16:00.418 --> 00:16:01.461
Hey!

307
00:16:01.544 --> 00:16:04.755
Nobody talks about Jett and Vineland
like that.

308
00:16:04.839 --> 00:16:07.592
Excuse me. Pardon. Hey. move out the way.

309
00:16:07.675 --> 00:16:08.676
I got next.

310
00:16:09.552 --> 00:16:10.761
Check up.

311
00:16:10.845 --> 00:16:12.472
Wait. wait. a goat?

312
00:16:15.391 --> 00:16:16.851
Thank you for the laugh. little dude.

313
00:16:16.934 --> 00:16:20.229
but why don't you just run on back
to the kiddie pool or something.

314
00:16:20.313 --> 00:16:21.439
Get you an ice cream.

315
00:16:21.522 --> 00:16:23.566
But. seriously. any takers?

316
00:16:24.192 --> 00:16:25.693
Even if I put money on it?

317
00:16:25.776 --> 00:16:27.487
First the shoes. now your rent money?

318
00:16:27.570 --> 00:16:29.489
Yes. Will. Commit.

319
00:16:29.572 --> 00:16:31.157
Mane. what are you gonna do now?

320
00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:32.950
Where's all the big talk now. Mane?

321
00:16:33.034 --> 00:16:34.535
Let's go. Vineland!

322
00:16:35.161 --> 00:16:39.499
So this is all the great Vineland
has to offer?

323
00:16:39.582 --> 00:16:42.084
A goat and some spare change?

324
00:16:43.085 --> 00:16:44.170
But you know what?

325
00:16:44.253 --> 00:16:46.964
Mane doesn't duck smoke so check up.

326
00:16:47.048 --> 00:16:48.341
Let's do it.

327
00:16:49.342 --> 00:16:51.385
Everything counts as one.

328
00:16:51.886 --> 00:16:52.929
First to three.

329
00:16:53.721 --> 00:16:54.639
Your ball.

330
00:17:02.271 --> 00:17:03.022
Oh. snap!

331
00:17:03.105 --> 00:17:04.106
That's one.

332
00:17:04.732 --> 00:17:05.983
I'd fight a big for that.

333
00:17:09.237 --> 00:17:11.197
So you do know how to pass.

334
00:17:11.280 --> 00:17:13.199
You gonna guard me
from all the way out there?

335
00:17:14.450 --> 00:17:15.743
Let's go.

336
00:17:16.285 --> 00:17:17.203
Come on.

337
00:17:20.248 --> 00:17:22.083
