00:52:35.527 --> 00:52:38.489
-Oh. hi!
-Oh. hi. Flo.

1018
00:52:38.572 --> 00:52:39.490
-Hey. Flo!
-Hi. Flo.

1019
00:52:39.573 --> 00:52:41.742
-Hey. boss.
-Hi. piglet.

1020
00:52:42.534 --> 00:52:43.744
Hi. Modo.

1021
00:52:43.827 --> 00:52:44.828
Anyways...

1022
00:52:45.537 --> 00:52:47.790
Great team win last night.

1023
00:52:47.873 --> 00:52:51.335
Socials are blowing up.
and I've got some exciting news.

1024
00:52:51.835 --> 00:52:53.504
Hey. is Jett there?

1025
00:52:53.587 --> 00:52:54.963
-Jett?
-What?

1026
00:52:55.047 --> 00:52:56.173
-Jett?
-What?

1027
00:52:56.256 --> 00:52:57.383
-Jett!
-What?

1028
00:52:57.466 --> 00:53:00.928
Oh. hi. You know that Jett promo tomorrow?

1029
00:53:01.011 --> 00:53:03.806
Well. now you're all gonna be in it.

1030
00:53:04.973 --> 00:53:07.851
Yeah. This is dope.

1031
00:53:17.528 --> 00:53:21.782
In Vineland. our roots run deep.

1032
00:53:22.574 --> 00:53:25.786
Vineland didn't just invent
the game of roarball.

1033
00:53:25.869 --> 00:53:27.705
We define it.

1034
00:53:28.372 --> 00:53:30.749
No one gets by me in the lane.

1035
00:53:30.833 --> 00:53:32.710
I don't play the long game.

1036
00:53:32.793 --> 00:53:34.545
I play the tall game.

1037
00:53:34.920 --> 00:53:36.880
Can't catch me on a fast break.

1038
00:53:38.132 --> 00:53:39.675
I make you feel weird

1039
00:53:40.175 --> 00:53:42.052
and you're not sure why.

1040
00:53:42.594 --> 00:53:44.096
And I'm the best in the game.

1041
00:53:44.179 --> 00:53:48.726
It's the end of one era
and the beginning of another.

1042
00:53:49.226 --> 00:53:51.353
It's my time now.

1043
00:53:51.437 --> 00:53:55.149
And now. it's time to pass the torch
to the new GO--

1044
00:53:56.233 --> 00:53:57.151
GOAT!

1045
00:54:00.237 --> 00:54:01.864
I'm sorry. I can't. I can't. I... This...

1046
00:54:01.947 --> 00:54:03.824
-My body is rejecting the word.
-Cut!

1047
00:54:03.907 --> 00:54:05.492
-You know what. let's just take five.
-Cut!

1048
00:54:05.576 --> 00:54:07.077
Jett. baby. what's the problem?

1049
00:54:07.161 --> 00:54:08.871
The problem is I'm the GOAT.

1050
00:54:08.954 --> 00:54:12.791
I'm not passing the torch
'cause I'm still playing.

1051
00:54:13.333 --> 00:54:16.003
It's just a promo. It's a play on words.

1052
00:54:16.086 --> 00:54:18.213
He's a goat but also wants to be the GOAT.

1053
00:54:18.297 --> 00:54:19.339
Just say the lines.

1054
00:54:19.423 --> 00:54:21.759
Are we all okay with this?

1055
00:54:21.842 --> 00:54:23.010
Now. I want to see a show of paws.

1056
00:54:23.093 --> 00:54:25.888
Raise 'em up! Who is okay with this?

1057
00:54:26.430 --> 00:54:28.140
Everybody? Okay.

1058
00:54:28.223 --> 00:54:31.101
Hey. Maximus. let's pick it up
from "they define it."

1059
00:54:31.727 --> 00:54:32.978
You got it. boss.

1060
00:54:33.979 --> 00:54:36.899
Vineland didn't just invent
the game of roarball.

1061
00:54:36.982 --> 00:54:38.484
We define it.

1062
00:54:38.567 --> 00:54:40.652
I block every shot.

1063
00:54:40.736 --> 00:54:43.197
I'm unstoppable. I think.

1064
00:54:43.280 --> 00:54:46.200
And I think there is
a power struggle happening.

1065
00:54:46.283 --> 00:54:48.452
-The end of one era...
-I'm the GOAT.

1066
00:54:48.535 --> 00:54:50.662
...and the beginning of another
that's even better.

1067
00:54:50.746 --> 00:54:51.747
It's my time--

1068
00:54:51.830 --> 00:54:52.956
-No. it's not.
-Cut!

1069
00:54:53.040 --> 00:54:54.124
Just say the line. Jett.

1070
00:54:54.208 --> 00:54:55.459
No! It's not true.

1071
00:54:55.542 --> 00:54:58.378
I don't think you understand the
difference between figurative and literal.

1072
00:54:58.462 --> 00:55:00.255
It's a double goat meaning.

1073
00:55:00.339 --> 00:55:01.924
I don't care. I'm not saying it!

1074
00:55:02.007 --> 00:55:03.425
And he's not saying it either!

1075
00:55:03.509 --> 00:55:06.637
And y'all don't even think
about saying it. Capisce?

1076
00:55:06.720 --> 00:55:09.640
Vineland didn't just invent
the game of roarball.

1077
00:55:09.723 --> 00:55:10.808
We define it.

1078
00:55:10.891 --> 00:55:13.602
I just wanna be a good dad.

1079
00:55:13.685 --> 00:55:15.979
I just wanna blow minds with sick rhymes.

1080
00:55:16.063 --> 00:55:19.775
Whoever memes my beak.
you will be hearing from my lawyer.

1081
00:55:19.858 --> 00:55:21.860
I don't even know the rules of roarball.

1082
00:55:21.944 --> 00:55:24.404
I'm the GOAT.
Always have been. always will be.

1083
00:55:24.488 --> 00:55:26.031
Not some little goat guy.

1084
00:55:26.114 --> 00:55:28.325
-It's a single goat meaning.
-Cut!

1085
00:55:28.408 --> 00:55:29.409
Cut. cut!

1086
00:55:29.493 --> 00:55:32.871
Look. since you're not gonna say the line.
why don't you just give us a little "Baa."

1087
00:55:32.955 --> 00:55:34.665
I am not saying that.

1088
00:55:34.748 --> 00:55:36.500
Why do I bother you so much?

1089
00:55:37.125 --> 00:55:39.795
You just got here. son. Who even are you?

1090
00:55:39.878 --> 00:55:42.297
I'm the one who stepped up
when you fouled out.

1091
00:55:42.381 --> 00:55:44.800
We finally won.
and you weren't even on the court.

1092
00:55:46.468 --> 00:55:47.678
Now I feel weird.

1093
00:55:47.761 --> 00:55:49.638
Is this how I make everyone feel?

1094
00:55:51.306 --> 00:55:52.641
You know what. superstar?

1095
00:55:52.724 --> 00:55:54.810
This looks like it's your promo now.

1096
00:55:54.893 --> 00:55:57.145
'Cause I'm out of here. Yeah.

1097
00:55:57.646 --> 00:55:58.814
Good luck selling tickets.

1098
00:56:02.109 --> 00:56:04.945
Jett! Wait. I'm sorry. I didn't mean to--

1099
00:56:05.028 --> 00:56:06.613
I didn't sign up for that. all right?

1100
00:56:06.697 --> 00:56:08.824
Come on. Jett. it's just a promo.

1101
00:56:08.907 --> 00:56:11.910
-It gets fans hyped for our game!
-But it's not.

1102
00:56:12.536 --> 00:56:14.121
It's how everyone treats me.

1103
00:56:14.621 --> 00:56:17.332
They all want me to pass the torch.
but I'm not done!

1104
00:56:17.416 --> 00:56:20.335
-There she is. Hey. Mom...
-I'm still here! I'm still playing!

1105
00:56:20.419 --> 00:56:22.379
We're still waiting
on that Claw. Fillmore.

1106
00:56:22.462 --> 00:56:23.839
You're better off on the bench.

1107
00:56:23.922 --> 00:56:25.007
-What?
-I love you. Jett!

1108
00:56:25.090 --> 00:56:27.759
-I just want my car. Where is my driver?
-Jett! Over here!

1109
00:56:27.843 --> 00:56:30.220
-Follow me.
-Jett Fillmore!

1110
00:56:30.304 --> 00:56:32.472
Hey. Jett. Why do you not win anymore?

1111
00:56:34.600 --> 00:56:35.767
Hey. watch it!

1112
00:56:38.937 --> 00:56:39.938
Excuse me.

1113
00:56:41.982 --> 00:56:43.233
This way.

1114
00:56:43.901 --> 00:56:45.527
This kid can move.

1115
00:57:00.918 --> 00:57:02.294
I've never broken the law before.

1116
00:57:03.003 --> 00:57:04.254
I feel so alive.

1117
00:57:04.338 --> 00:57:06.423
I actually paid for both of our rides.

1118
00:57:06.506 --> 00:57:08.050
I just wanted to see you sweat.

1119
00:57:13.639 --> 00:57:15.265
It was so messed up back there.

1120
00:57:15.349 --> 00:57:18.018
I mean. they act like
you've been losing forever!

1121
00:57:18.101 --> 00:57:21.063
I don't know what's wrong with them.
but I remember the Furball game.

1122
00:57:21.146 --> 00:57:23.857
That was amazing! You scored 70 points!

1123
00:57:23.941 --> 00:57:26.360
Well. you know why they call it
the Furball game. right?

1124
00:57:27.319 --> 00:57:30.697
Because I choked. I missed the last shot.

1125
00:57:31.365 --> 00:57:32.574
We didn't make the Claw.

1126
00:57:33.492 --> 00:57:37.454
Ever since then. Vineland's got
no love for Jett Fillmore.

1127
00:57:37.537 --> 00:57:39.081
No love for Jett Fillmore?

1128
00:57:39.915 --> 00:57:42.292
You're seriously gonna listen
to a couple of haters?

1129
00:57:42.376 --> 00:57:44.211
Where's the lie? Even I get it.

1130
00:57:44.836 --> 00:57:47.422
Next stop. Vineland City Center.

1131
00:57:47.506 --> 00:57:48.882
Okay. Get up.

1132
00:57:48.966 --> 00:57:50.550
We're getting off right here.

1133
00:58:00.978 --> 00:58:02.938
Hey. there he is!

1134
00:58:04.106 --> 00:58:06.608
You come to pick up some extra shifts?

1135
00:58:07.651 --> 00:58:08.819
I see you got jokes.

1136
00:58:08.902 --> 00:58:10.237
Come back empty-handed?

1137
00:58:10.320 --> 00:58:13.699
You said you'd get me
Jett Fillmore's autograph.

1138
00:58:13.782 --> 00:58:15.867
Oh. my gosh. It's Jett Fillmore.

1139
00:58:15.951 --> 00:58:16.952
What's up. y'all?

1140
00:58:17.035 --> 00:58:20.414
Jett said she'd never tried the pie.
so I figured we'd pull up.

1141
00:58:22.332 --> 00:58:23.583
This is...

1142
00:58:27.421 --> 00:58:28.672
Not bad. huh?

1143
00:58:31.216 --> 00:58:33.593
Wait. is that my high school jersey?

1144
00:58:33.677 --> 00:58:36.972
Dang. y'all are some crazy stalkers.

1145
00:58:42.477 --> 00:58:44.855
What do we have here? No way.

1146
00:58:44.938 --> 00:58:46.023
Is that you?

1147
00:58:47.733 --> 00:58:49.985
Hey. you wanna meet the others?

1148
00:58:51.194 --> 00:58:56.908
My grandpappy came here from afar
to help build the Greenhouse. Yes.

1149
00:58:56.992 --> 00:59:00.078
That's little me right there in my diaper.

1150
00:59:00.162 --> 00:59:01.663
Wow.

1151
00:59:01.747 --> 00:59:03.373
We're gonna name our baby after you. Jett!

1152
00:59:03.457 --> 00:59:05.375
We're hoping she'll grow up
to be just like you.

1153
00:59:06.418 --> 00:59:07.586
Cute egg.

1154
00:59:07.669 --> 00:59:08.670
Check this out!

1155
00:59:08.754 --> 00:59:10.881
When I move my shoulders.
it looks like you're dunking.

1156
00:59:10.964 --> 00:59:12.424
Oh. yeah.

1157
00:59:13.258 --> 00:59:16.094
It definitely looks like
I am doing something.

1158
00:59:17.095 --> 00:59:18.388
Okay. so we're down by two. right?

1159
00:59:18.472 --> 00:59:20.182
I'm nauseous.

1160
00:59:20.265 --> 00:59:22.142
It's like that every time
I go to open my mouth.

1161
00:59:22.225 --> 00:59:23.602
it's like... here it comes.

1162
00:59:23.685 --> 00:59:25.520
-I can't even see straight.
-I knew it! I knew it!

1163
00:59:25.604 --> 00:59:26.855
I could tell something was off.

1164
00:59:26.938 --> 00:59:28.190
How did you get so sick?

1165
00:59:28.273 --> 00:59:31.318
Look. I'm not gonna say it's true.

1166
00:59:31.401 --> 00:59:35.822
but I will say the delivery guy
was wearing a Magma jersey.

1167
00:59:35.906 --> 00:59:37.491
Coinkydink? You decide.

1168
00:59:37.574 --> 00:59:39.993
Drumroll. please.

1169
00:59:43.413 --> 00:59:44.998
Right? Right? I told you.

1170
00:59:45.540 --> 00:59:47.918
Oh. snap. The Fillmore 1's?

1171
00:59:48.001 --> 00:59:49.294
Where did you get these?

1172
00:59:49.377 --> 00:59:52.255
A collector never reveals her secrets.

1173
00:59:52.756 --> 00:59:55.717
Just kidding. I got 'em from the store
when they came out.

1174
00:59:55.801 --> 00:59:57.594
I've been looking everywhere for these.

1175
00:59:57.677 --> 00:59:59.054
Okay. how much do you want for 'em?

1176
00:59:59.137 --> 01:00:00.263
Are you kidding me?

1177
01:00:00.347 --> 01:00:01.556
Your money's no good here.

1178
01:00:01.640 --> 01:00:04.142
They're your shoe. Just take 'em.

1179
01:00:04.226 --> 01:00:05.644
No. No.

1180
01:00:05.727 --> 01:00:08.063
Just bring back a Claw.

1181
01:00:09.022 --> 01:00:09.856
Deal.

1182
01:00:10.565 --> 01:00:11.858
Bye. Jett!

1183
01:00:11.942 --> 01:00:13.068
Later. y'all.

1184
01:00:13.151 --> 01:00:14.778
How did you know about that spot?

1185
01:00:14.861 --> 01:00:16.863
I go there for the pie.

1186
01:00:16.947 --> 01:00:19.658
It delivers every time.

1187
01:00:21.284 --> 01:00:22.494
You were the delivery boy.

1188
01:00:22.577 --> 01:00:26.039
Yeah. yeah. Was that a little too obvious?

1189
01:00:26.123 --> 01:00:27.249
Okay.

1190
01:00:28.458 --> 01:00:29.584
I mean...

1191
01:00:32.129 --> 01:00:35.340
The real reason I know the diner
is because my mom used to work there.

1192
01:00:35.841 --> 01:00:38.009
She was a huge Thorns fan.

1193
01:00:38.093 --> 01:00:39.803
-Mom.
-That's for every year.

1194
01:00:40.303 --> 01:00:42.514
Happy birthday. Will.

1195
01:00:43.348 --> 01:00:48.353
Baby. you know you could wish
for anything. so dream big.

1196
01:00:48.854 --> 01:00:51.022
You're not just going to play roarball.

1197
01:00:51.773 --> 01:00:53.775
You're gonna change the game.

1198
01:00:55.735 --> 01:00:57.112
Dream big.

1199
01:01:01.700 --> 01:01:04.286
Then. she got sick.

1200
01:01:08.665 --> 01:01:11.126
And Vineland stepped up for me.

1201
01:01:13.503 --> 01:01:18.592
Roarball was where I went
to get out of my head and just... play.

1202
01:01:19.092 --> 01:01:20.343
You know?

1203
01:01:20.427 --> 01:01:24.639
And everyone thought I was tripping when
I said I wanted to be a roarball player.

1204
01:01:25.140 --> 01:01:28.351
Everybody. Except for my mom.

1205
01:01:32.772 --> 01:01:35.483
And I want her to be right.

1206
01:01:41.072 --> 01:01:43.074
You got a lot of good folks behind you.

1207
01:01:45.452 --> 01:01:46.578
So do you.

1208
01:01:52.626 --> 01:01:54.085
See you at practice tomorrow.

1209
01:02:11.144 --> 01:02:13.772
Hey. yo. It's Mane season.

1210
01:02:13.855 --> 01:02:15.482
Oh. no. Here we go.

1211
01:02:15.565 --> 01:02:18.318
And you know. man. just at the barbershop
with P-Dogg and Boogie.

1212
01:02:18.401 --> 01:02:19.402
Let's get into it.

1213
01:02:19.486 --> 01:02:21.821
A lot of naysayers out there. folks.

1214
01:02:21.905 --> 01:02:24.282
been talkin' about this big game
the goat had.

1215
01:02:24.366 --> 01:02:27.285
Puttin' up a whole three points.
He's trash.

1216
01:02:27.369 --> 01:02:29.162
Thorns are trash! Thorns are trash!

1217
01:02:29.246 --> 01:02:31.122
And it ain't just the goat that's wack.

1218
01:02:31.206 --> 01:02:32.832
The whole team is cooked!

1219
01:02:32.916 --> 01:02:34.209
They trash.

1220
01:02:34.292 --> 01:02:37.003
Someone needs to shut this clown up
once and for all.

1221
01:02:37.087 --> 01:02:39.547
Hold up! Looks like we got
a special chat request.

1222
01:02:40.465 --> 01:02:43.593
It's the grand mama herself. Jett Fillmore.

1223
01:02:43.677 --> 01:02:46.888
Yo. yo. yo! Mane is on live with Jett!

1224
01:02:46.972 --> 01:02:48.181
What? Let me see that.

1225
01:02:49.849 --> 01:02:51.726
No way. bro-dents.

1226
01:02:51.810 --> 01:02:55.313
Do you know what? I'm just surprised
you even know how to use your phone

1227
01:02:55.397 --> 01:02:58.525
for anything other than reading a menu
with the flashlight.

1228
01:02:58.608 --> 01:03:00.402
I'm surprised you can talk
with teeth like that.

1229
01:03:00.485 --> 01:03:02.445
Your tongue over there
lookin' like it's in jail.

1230
01:03:02.529 --> 01:03:03.822
"Let me out. Let me out."

1231
01:03:04.948 --> 01:03:06.866
Jett's got bars.

1232
01:03:06.950 --> 01:03:09.077
I've been in the league five years.

1233
01:03:09.160 --> 01:03:10.870
already got two Claws.

1234
01:03:10.954 --> 01:03:12.247
How many Claws you got?

1235
01:03:12.330 --> 01:03:14.582
-Nada.
-Ball don't lie. Ball don't lie.

1236
01:03:14.666 --> 01:03:16.001
Well. that's about to change.

1237
01:03:16.084 --> 01:03:20.213
I don't know if you saw our last game.
but Will is shooting straight fire.

1238
01:03:20.297 --> 01:03:21.298
Archie is a beast.

1239
01:03:21.381 --> 01:03:23.174
Olivia got her confidence back.

1240
01:03:23.258 --> 01:03:24.259
Lenny's a stopper

1241
01:03:24.342 --> 01:03:25.635
-and Modo is an icon.
-Hey!

1242
01:03:25.719 --> 01:03:27.595
The Thorns are about to win
our next eight games

1243
01:03:27.679 --> 01:03:29.597
and then. yeah. we're coming for the Claw.

1244
01:03:30.932 --> 01:03:32.100
Girl. you crazy.

1245
01:03:32.183 --> 01:03:35.729
Only thing crazy is that Clydesdale hair
that you got sewn into your head.

1246
01:03:35.812 --> 01:03:37.355
Yeah. the textures don't match.

1247
01:03:37.439 --> 01:03:38.857
Drag him. Jett.

1248
01:03:40.025 --> 01:03:42.777
-Textures don't match.
-Hey. guys. don't diss the hair.

1249
01:03:42.861 --> 01:03:44.070
You know I get sensitive.

1250
01:03:44.154 --> 01:03:44.988
Jett!

1251
01:03:45.071 --> 01:03:46.489
Wait till I get off this live.

1252
01:03:46.573 --> 01:03:49.659
You know what. I hope you make a run
so I can wreck you.

1253
01:03:49.743 --> 01:03:52.245
just like I wrecked that baby goat
at the Cage.

1254
01:03:52.329 --> 01:03:55.248
Until then. keep Will and the Thorns
out your mouth.

1255
01:03:55.332 --> 01:03:56.458
These roots run deep!

1256
01:03:56.958 --> 01:03:58.084
Fillmore out.

1257
01:03:59.419 --> 01:04:00.462
These roots run deep!

1258
01:04:00.545 --> 01:04:02.380
Roots run deep! Roots run deep!

1259
01:04:02.464 --> 01:04:03.590
Roots run deep!

1260
01:04:03.673 --> 01:04:06.885
Roots run deep! Roots run deep!
Roots run deep!

1261
01:04:13.475 --> 01:04:14.893
Yeah. mama!

1262
01:04:16.895 --> 01:04:19.272
You said some pretty nice stuff about us.

1263
01:04:19.814 --> 01:04:21.149
I'm wondering why.

1264
01:04:21.232 --> 01:04:22.275
Are you feeling okay?

1265
01:04:22.359 --> 01:04:25.820
It's the first time I've been tagged
in something that didn't make me cry.

1266
01:04:26.321 --> 01:04:27.989
I don't trust it.

1267
01:04:28.073 --> 01:04:29.574
Did you mean it?

1268
01:04:30.825 --> 01:04:33.578
Look. I meant every word that I said.

1269
01:04:33.661 --> 01:04:35.163
I really do need y'all.

1270
01:04:35.246 --> 01:04:38.208
And it's time I finally acknowledged

1271
01:04:38.291 --> 01:04:41.252
that I've got some really good folks
behind me.

1272
01:04:41.795 --> 01:04:43.713
-Yeah.
-Really?

1273
01:04:43.797 --> 01:04:47.300
To show you how serious I am.
I'm ready to shake some things up.

1274
01:04:49.344 --> 01:04:53.807
I'm officially naming Dennis
the new head coach of the Thorns.

1275
01:04:55.892 --> 01:04:58.478
But I'm already head coach.

1276
01:04:58.561 --> 01:05:01.106
I know. But now. it's. like.
for real this time.

1277
01:05:01.189 --> 01:05:02.816
You're gonna be head coach. Only coach.

1278
01:05:04.317 --> 01:05:05.735
The team is yours. Dennis.

1279
01:05:06.528 --> 01:05:08.029
Yeah. man!

1280
01:05:09.239 --> 01:05:10.657
Let's go. baby. Give it up.

1281
01:05:10.740 --> 01:05:12.909
My therapist said this day
would never come.

1282
01:05:13.493 --> 01:05:14.536
Just give me a second.

1283
01:05:15.036 --> 01:05:17.330
Dennis. get it together. Get it together.

1284
01:05:17.414 --> 01:05:19.332
Get. It. Together.

1285
01:05:24.504 --> 01:05:29.551
I've been watching. learning.
waiting for this day.

1286
01:05:29.634 --> 01:05:31.136
-I'm scared.
-We like it.

1287
01:05:31.219 --> 01:05:35.807
We are going to rip the heart
out of this league

1288
01:05:35.890 --> 01:05:37.559
and make 'em look at it.

1289
01:05:37.642 --> 01:05:38.935
Nice.

1290
01:05:39.018 --> 01:05:43.815
Welcome to Dennis's world of pain.

1291
01:05:47.318 --> 01:05:50.071
Archie. you don't have to worry
about your little girls

1292
01:05:50.155 --> 01:05:51.656
growing up with violent tendencies.

1293
01:05:51.739 --> 01:05:53.324
Charge!

1294
01:05:53.408 --> 01:05:56.995
They've gone full-tilt
365-days-a-year psychopath.

1295
01:05:57.078 --> 01:05:59.664
Actually. it's 364.

1296
01:05:59.747 --> 01:06:01.291
We take Christmas off.

1297
01:06:01.374 --> 01:06:03.084
Stop thinking of yourself as an enforcer.

1298
01:06:03.168 --> 01:06:05.253
You're a protector.

1299
01:06:05.336 --> 01:06:08.173
Your teammates are like
your daughters too.

1300
01:06:08.256 --> 01:06:09.257
Protect them.

1301
01:06:09.340 --> 01:06:11.468
Hey. hands off my beautiful daughter.

1302
01:06:11.551 --> 01:06:12.635
Good looking out. Archie.

1303
01:06:12.719 --> 01:06:14.053
Wait. what did you just call me?

1304
01:06:14.971 --> 01:06:19.642
Lenny. team after team used you
for your height and threw you away.

1305
01:06:19.726 --> 01:06:21.394
So you lost your drive.

1306
01:06:21.478 --> 01:06:23.688
Ten teams in ten years. Coach.

1307
01:06:23.771 --> 01:06:26.191
Well. this team has your back.

1308
01:06:26.274 --> 01:06:28.485
So stick your neck out for them.

1309
01:06:28.568 --> 01:06:30.653
Now tear the roof off this mother!

1310
01:06:36.201 --> 01:06:37.035
Bang!

1311
01:06:37.118 --> 01:06:39.871
-Nice one. Lenny.
-That's my squad.

1312
01:06:39.954 --> 01:06:42.749
That's my squad. I kind of like that.

1313
01:06:42.832 --> 01:06:43.750
Olivia.

1314
01:06:43.833 --> 01:06:45.460
One second. I'm just...

1315
01:06:45.543 --> 01:06:46.961
-Seriously. give me your phone.
-Oh. no.

1316
01:06:47.045 --> 01:06:48.588
You are never seeing it again.

1317
01:06:50.006 --> 01:06:51.049
Another phone?

1318
01:06:51.132 --> 01:06:53.676
Where are you getting all these phones?

1319
01:06:53.760 --> 01:06:57.847
Olivia. get your head out of the phone
and into the game!

1320
01:07:00.517 --> 01:07:03.228
You were drafted number one for a reason.

1321
01:07:03.311 --> 01:07:05.939
The only thing holding you back is you.

1322
01:07:06.022 --> 01:07:08.775
You are still that bird.

1323
01:07:13.029 --> 01:07:15.114
I am that bird.

1324
01:07:15.990 --> 01:07:17.408
Will. Jett.

1325
01:07:17.492 --> 01:07:19.953
I'm gonna coach the scat out of you.

1326
01:07:20.036 --> 01:07:22.205
-Dennis. there's kids here.
-Scat! Scat! Scat!

1327
01:07:22.288 --> 01:07:26.584
Jett. remember these three words.
"Pass the ball."

1328
01:07:26.668 --> 01:07:28.920
-Like. let the ball go?
-Jett.

1329
01:07:29.003 --> 01:07:31.339
You mean share? With the others?

1330
01:07:31.422 --> 01:07:32.715
I don't think this lesson is for me.

1331
01:07:32.799 --> 01:07:34.300
-Trust your team.
-Open!

1332
01:07:34.384 --> 01:07:35.718
Jett. pass the ball.

1333
01:07:36.594 --> 01:07:38.638
-It's harder than it looks.
-I'm open.

1334
01:07:39.472 --> 01:07:40.682
-Pass it!
-What?

1335
01:07:42.517 --> 01:07:43.893
-Jett.
-I got it. I got it.

1336
01:07:43.977 --> 01:07:45.812
-Pass the ball. Jett.
-No. no. no. no.

1337
01:07:45.895 --> 01:07:49.274
Dennis. No. no. Dennis.
No. no. no. Dennis!

1338
01:07:53.778 --> 01:07:55.154
Yes! Yes!

1339
01:07:55.238 --> 01:07:58.116
Now just do that 500.000 more times.

1340
01:07:58.199 --> 01:07:59.659
You. big hairy guy.

1341
01:07:59.742 --> 01:08:01.786
Block everything that
the kid throws your way.

1342
01:08:01.869 --> 01:08:06.165
And you. that's 12 feet of grizzly.
Figure it out.

1343
01:08:07.041 --> 01:08:08.042
Blocked.

1344
01:08:09.669 --> 01:08:11.045
-Blocked.
-Dang.

1345
01:08:11.546 --> 01:08:12.547
-Hey.
-Blocked.

1346
01:08:13.840 --> 01:08:15.216
Blocked.

1347
01:08:15.300 --> 01:08:19.095
Will. you gotta find a way
to get your shot over him.

1348
01:08:19.178 --> 01:08:20.013
And Modo--

1349
01:08:20.096 --> 01:08:22.682
Wait. wait. Say it with your mind.

1350
01:08:23.349 --> 01:08:25.143
Message!

1351
01:08:25.226 --> 01:08:26.227
Yeah. yeah.

1352
01:08:27.687 --> 01:08:29.188
Received.

1353
01:08:29.272 --> 01:08:31.649
If you do all this.
you'll be more than a team.

1354
01:08:31.733 --> 01:08:34.444
You'll be a unit. Unstoppable.

1355
01:08:34.527 --> 01:08:35.612
Roots run deep!

1356
01:08:35.695 --> 01:08:38.781
"Goat Tears" is wack.
and I can't let it stand.

1357
01:08:38.865 --> 01:08:42.660
So. Will. I've prepared a little something

1358
01:08:42.744 --> 01:08:44.954
to say "thank you"
for pushing us this far.

1359
01:08:45.955 --> 01:08:47.290
That's my squad. that's my squad

1360
01:08:47.373 --> 01:08:49.667
Here you go. Ms. Fillmore.
Can I get a picture?

1361
01:08:50.835 --> 01:08:53.630
Shout out to my squad
Throw me the alley-oop

1362
01:08:53.713 --> 01:08:55.006
I'm always at the top...

1363
01:08:55.089 --> 01:08:56.341
No way.

1364
01:08:56.424 --> 01:08:57.759
Nice to meet you. Theo.

1365
01:08:57.842 --> 01:09:00.261
And this is for your dad.

1366
01:09:01.346 --> 01:09:03.056
We not horsin' round with you. okay

1367
01:09:03.139 --> 01:09:05.892
Uno reverse. You like that. Modo?

1368
01:09:05.975 --> 01:09:07.185
-Give me some.
-Uno.

1369
01:09:07.268 --> 01:09:09.020
Sorry. horsey. gotta roast ya

1370
01:09:09.103 --> 01:09:10.647
Looks like Mr. Pony turnin' into Mr. Phony

1371
01:09:10.730 --> 01:09:11.731
Will.

1372
01:09:11.814 --> 01:09:15.318
Lenny G the one and only
And I always got my homeys

1373
01:09:15.401 --> 01:09:16.944
Slamalamadingdong!

1374
01:09:17.028 --> 01:09:19.238
That's my squad. hey
That's my squad. hey

1375
01:09:19.322 --> 01:09:20.239
Olivia.

1376
01:09:20.323 --> 01:09:21.741
I love my squad. hey

1377
01:09:21.824 --> 01:09:22.950
Yo. Lenny!

1378
01:09:24.369 --> 01:09:27.246
Shout out to my squad
Throw me the alley-oop

1379
01:09:27.330 --> 01:09:30.750
I'm always at the top
"Cause I'm taller than the hoop

1380
01:09:30.833 --> 01:09:32.043
Horns on. everybody.

1381
01:09:32.126 --> 01:09:34.379
Thorns have really found their groove.

1382
01:09:34.462 --> 01:09:37.131
And is it me. or is Modo looking
different these days?

1383
01:09:37.215 --> 01:09:39.759
Oh. yeah. He's a thirst trap. Chuck.

1384
01:09:39.842 --> 01:09:41.344
Go long for my skin.

1385
01:09:41.427 --> 01:09:42.804
Marry me. Modo.

1386
01:09:42.887 --> 01:09:44.180
No. marry me!

1387
01:09:44.764 --> 01:09:46.057
Thorns! Thorns!

1388
01:09:46.140 --> 01:09:48.768
The Thorns punch their ticket
to the Roar Four

1389
01:09:48.851 --> 01:09:50.436
and are heading to the playoffs.

1390
01:09:50.520 --> 01:09:52.605
What a turnaround. Chuck!

1391
01:09:52.689 --> 01:09:55.525
If I were Mane. I'd be shaking
in my horseshoes

1392
01:09:55.608 --> 01:09:57.819
'cause the Thorns are coming for him.

1393
01:09:57.902 --> 01:10:01.280
Looks like Mr. Pony
Turnin' into Mr. Phony...

1394
01:10:01.364 --> 01:10:02.740
Do we have a deal?

1395
01:10:04.742 --> 01:10:05.743
Good.

1396
01:10:05.827 --> 01:10:09.247
Coach Dennis. how about a comment
on this team's epic turnaround?

1397
01:10:09.330 --> 01:10:10.581
How's it feel. Dennis?

1398
01:10:10.665 --> 01:10:13.418
It feels like victory!

1399
01:10:22.552 --> 01:10:23.553
Yay!

1400
01:10:23.636 --> 01:10:27.432
Okay. didn't know an ostrich
could get that fly. I see you. Olivia.

1401
01:10:27.515 --> 01:10:31.978
You know what they say.
birds of a feather look fly together.

1402
01:10:33.104 --> 01:10:35.189
Archie's a whole vibe.

1403
01:10:35.732 --> 01:10:39.318
Yeah. buddy. I look good and I play good.

1404
01:10:40.695 --> 01:10:44.699
If Modo were any more of a snack.
he'd eat himself.

1405
01:10:44.782 --> 01:10:46.659
Love it. Love it.

1406
01:10:48.661 --> 01:10:50.121
I'll be right back.

1407
01:10:51.205 --> 01:10:53.082
Anyone know where Jett is?

1408
01:10:53.166 --> 01:10:54.167
I'll go get her.

1409
01:10:54.792 --> 01:10:58.921
From the Vineland Thorns. at guard.
Jett Fillmore!

1410
01:10:59.005 --> 01:11:00.548
I sold this team.

1411
01:11:01.215 --> 01:11:04.802
The new Thorns are relocating
to Sunken City.

1412
01:11:04.886 --> 01:11:07.847
I'm sorry. what? You're joking.

1413
01:11:07.930 --> 01:11:11.267
I never joke about money. honey.

1414
01:11:11.350 --> 01:11:14.145
I brought Will onto this team
to put butts in seats.

1415
01:11:14.228 --> 01:11:17.064
but I didn't expect
for you to actually win.

1416
01:11:17.148 --> 01:11:19.150
I'm selling while the getting's good.

1417
01:11:19.984 --> 01:11:21.569
What's gonna happen to the team?

1418
01:11:22.111 --> 01:11:26.532
They're all gone. sweetie. Cleaning house.

1419
01:11:26.616 --> 01:11:28.534
And as for you...

1420
01:11:30.244 --> 01:11:36.459
I made sure the new owners knew
all about your worn-out body.

1421
01:11:36.542 --> 01:11:41.506
And surprise. surprise.
they weren't about to waste money

1422
01:11:41.589 --> 01:11:44.801
on an old. broken-down player

1423
01:11:44.884 --> 01:11:48.012
who's never gonna win a Claw!

1424
01:11:49.472 --> 01:11:53.935
And tell the team to clean out
their lockers after y'all lose.

1425
01:11:54.018 --> 01:11:57.730
Enjoy your early retirement. Jett.

1426
01:11:58.356 --> 01:12:00.900
Hey. good luck out there tonight.

1427
01:12:04.987 --> 01:12:07.114
Jett. Flo sold the Thorns?

1428
01:12:07.198 --> 01:12:09.492
-You listening in on my conversations now?
-We need to go tell the team.

1429
01:12:09.575 --> 01:12:11.202
No. we'll tell them after the game.

1430
01:12:11.285 --> 01:12:13.120
If we tell them now. they'll fall apart.

1431
01:12:13.204 --> 01:12:14.288
This affects all of us.

1432
01:12:14.372 --> 01:12:16.791
Whatever's coming.
we got to face it together.

1433
01:12:16.874 --> 01:12:19.168
Who's team captain here? You or me?

1434
01:12:19.252 --> 01:12:21.462
-Jett.
-After the game.

1435
01:12:25.132 --> 01:12:27.134
Welcome to the Cryosphere.

1436
01:12:27.218 --> 01:12:31.764
Tonight. the Shivers face the Thorns
in the semi-final game.

1437
01:12:31.848 --> 01:12:34.267
The winner marches
triumphantly to the finals

1438
01:12:34.350 --> 01:12:37.895
to battle for a championship
and eternal glory.

1439
01:12:37.979 --> 01:12:41.274
The loser?
Banished to the cold void of history.

1440
01:12:41.357 --> 01:12:42.942
This is not just a game.

1441
01:12:43.025 --> 01:12:44.819
It is a reckoning.

1442
01:12:51.909 --> 01:12:54.912
Lenny. are you trying to get traded?

1443
01:12:54.996 --> 01:12:56.289
Hey. hey. Jett. you good?

1444
01:12:56.372 --> 01:12:57.790
Focus on the game.

1445
01:12:58.291 --> 01:13:00.209
Don't worry about it.
We'll get the next one.

1446
01:13:01.627 --> 01:13:02.628
Olivia.

1447
01:13:03.421 --> 01:13:04.338
One more pass.

1448
01:13:04.422 --> 01:13:06.549
Next time you think about shooting. don't.

1449
01:13:07.341 --> 01:13:09.051
I'm sorry. Jett.

1450
01:13:09.135 --> 01:13:10.720
And that's the half.

1451
01:13:12.763 --> 01:13:13.764
Maybe we should tell them now.

1452
01:13:13.848 --> 01:13:15.516
After the game.

1453
01:13:24.233 --> 01:13:25.693
Don't hurt yourself. grandma.

1454
01:13:25.776 --> 01:13:28.237
Catch! Yeah!

1455
01:13:30.239 --> 01:13:32.116
The icebreaker!

1456
01:13:32.199 --> 01:13:34.327
And Harris is slow to get up.

1457
01:13:34.410 --> 01:13:36.037
So much for that Claw.

1458
01:13:36.120 --> 01:13:36.954
Thanks.

1459
01:13:37.038 --> 01:13:39.457
Thorns are down by 15
late in the fourth quarter.

1460
01:13:39.540 --> 01:13:42.376
It is not looking good
for their playoff hopes.

1461
01:13:43.044 --> 01:13:45.087
What is going on out there?

1462
01:13:45.171 --> 01:13:47.673
Jett. tell them. They need to know.

1463
01:13:47.757 --> 01:13:48.799
What did I say?

1464
01:13:48.883 --> 01:13:51.135
Flo sold the team to Sunken City.

1465
01:13:51.218 --> 01:13:53.387
None of us are going with it.

1466
01:13:53.471 --> 01:13:54.805
Can she even do that?
Is that even allowed?

1467
01:13:54.889 --> 01:13:56.641
We were playing well.
We just started jelling.

1468
01:13:56.724 --> 01:13:58.893
-She sold our team?
-There are rules.

1469
01:13:58.976 --> 01:14:01.270
-I thought you had a championship.
-Could have been a legend. instead...

1470
01:14:01.354 --> 01:14:06.275
Broken-down player
who's never gonna win a Claw!

1471
01:14:06.359 --> 01:14:08.319
Just get me the ball.

1472
01:14:08.402 --> 01:14:10.237
I'm not going out like this.

1473
01:14:10.321 --> 01:14:12.281
Don't you mean "we"?

1474
01:14:12.365 --> 01:14:14.450
I know that look.

1475
01:14:18.871 --> 01:14:20.623
What do you think you're doing?

1476
01:14:21.332 --> 01:14:23.084
That's two. Thorns down by ten.

1477
01:14:23.167 --> 01:14:24.377
Come on.

1478
01:14:24.877 --> 01:14:26.003
We got to D up.

1479
01:14:27.046 --> 01:14:28.589
Somebody get a body on her.

1480
01:14:29.757 --> 01:14:30.841
Come on.

1481
01:14:32.134 --> 01:14:34.929
-Pass!
-We've seen this before. Rusty.

1482
01:14:35.012 --> 01:14:37.974
It's the Jett Fillmore show now.

1483
01:14:38.057 --> 01:14:39.976
Jett with the pull-up. Thorns down eight.

1484
01:14:43.020 --> 01:14:44.146
Heads up!

1485
01:14:46.148 --> 01:14:47.942
That deficit is cut to five.

1486
01:14:49.652 --> 01:14:51.153
It's a one-point game.

1487
01:14:51.237 --> 01:14:54.198
<i>-Ball! Now!
-It all comes down to this!</i>

1488
01:14:54.281 --> 01:14:56.033
-Archie!
-Give me that. small.

1489
01:14:56.117 --> 01:14:57.368
Boost me!

1490
01:14:59.537 --> 01:15:01.914
Will Harris for the win!

1491
01:15:05.626 --> 01:15:06.711
Yeah!

1492
01:15:06.794 --> 01:15:09.714
Thorns win! Thorns win!

1493
01:15:09.797 --> 01:15:11.966
They're headed to the Claw!

1494
01:15:16.971 --> 01:15:18.639
So it looks like we're going to the...

1495
01:15:20.891 --> 01:15:21.976
to the finals.

1496
01:15:25.312 --> 01:15:28.566
Wow. I'm done. Team's sold anyway.

1497
01:15:28.649 --> 01:15:30.651
-Come on. girls.
-I'm not sticking around for this.

1498
01:15:30.735 --> 01:15:31.944
Modo as well.

1499
01:15:36.657 --> 01:15:38.743
You used to be my favorite player.

1500
01:15:39.618 --> 01:15:40.745
Until today.

1501
01:15:41.996 --> 01:15:43.789
What a turn of events.

1502
01:15:43.873 --> 01:15:48.461
The Thorns have a shot at the Claw.
but Vineland has lost their team.

1503
01:15:48.544 --> 01:15:50.880
I'll tell you. Rusty.
I would hate to be a Thorns fan

1504
01:15:50.963 --> 01:15:52.173
right about now.

1505
01:17:07.498 --> 01:17:09.250
Come on. Let's go!

1506
01:17:10.459 --> 01:17:11.293
I got it!

1507
01:17:12.044 --> 01:17:13.045
Yeah!

1508
01:17:13.546 --> 01:17:14.839
Smalls can ball.

1509
01:17:15.923 --> 01:17:17.049
Yeah!

1510
01:17:18.634 --> 01:17:19.760
-Wait. is that...
-No way.

1511
01:17:19.844 --> 01:17:20.928
-Hey. Will.
-Hey. Will.

1512
01:17:21.762 --> 01:17:23.556
Goat? Ball.

1513
01:17:25.516 --> 01:17:27.852
Yo. shouldn't you be getting ready
to face the Magma?

1514
01:17:27.935 --> 01:17:29.645
Did you not watch the game?

1515
01:17:29.728 --> 01:17:31.856
I don't think Jett
wants to play with us anymore.

1516
01:17:32.398 --> 01:17:34.108
I'm willing to bet she does.

1517
01:17:35.609 --> 01:17:37.903
Hey. Can we talk?

1518
01:17:37.987 --> 01:17:38.988
I'm busy.

1519
01:17:39.071 --> 01:17:40.197
-No. he's not.
-Come on. come on.

1520
01:17:40.281 --> 01:17:42.950
-Give... Give me the ball.
-No. Not happening. My ball now.

1521
01:17:44.952 --> 01:17:48.455
I came to say I'm-I'm sorry.

1522
01:17:48.539 --> 01:17:50.708
Okay. Well. you did it. So...

1523
01:17:50.791 --> 01:17:53.711
Please. just hear me out.

1524
01:17:58.632 --> 01:18:00.593
I want to win.

1525
01:18:01.594 --> 01:18:03.012
I want to hold up that Claw

1526
01:18:03.095 --> 01:18:06.640
and feel what it's like
to be one of the greats.

1527
01:18:07.600 --> 01:18:10.644
When Flo said all that stuff
about me being washed-up.

1528
01:18:11.145 --> 01:18:12.521
it just... it-it...

1529
01:18:13.355 --> 01:18:14.648
it just got in my head.

1530
01:18:15.274 --> 01:18:19.403
And I couldn't let it go
because deep down. deep. deep down.

1531
01:18:20.237 --> 01:18:21.947
I'm scared she's right.

1532
01:18:22.573 --> 01:18:24.033
And I just panicked.

1533
01:18:24.909 --> 01:18:26.869
And I did you all so dirty.

1534
01:18:26.952 --> 01:18:30.456
And I'm so sorry.

1535
01:18:34.084 --> 01:18:35.878
You know. I really thought that

1536
01:18:35.961 --> 01:18:38.547
if I was holding a Claw
at the end of the day.

1537
01:18:38.631 --> 01:18:40.799
it wouldn't matter how I got it.

1538
01:18:40.883 --> 01:18:42.468
But when you think about it.

1539
01:18:42.551 --> 01:18:44.762
that's kind of all that matters.

1540
01:18:46.222 --> 01:18:49.350
That was a really good apology.

1541
01:18:49.433 --> 01:18:53.520
But you know.
you still owe the diner a Claw.

1542
01:18:54.521 --> 01:18:56.774
It's gonna be hard to win without a team.

1543
01:18:56.857 --> 01:18:58.859
I might know a few folks.

1544
01:18:59.985 --> 01:19:01.737
-Dad.
-Daddy clown!

1545
01:19:01.820 --> 01:19:03.322
Oh. thank God.

1546
01:19:03.405 --> 01:19:04.782
-These girls are crazy.
-Daddy. Daddy.

1547
01:19:04.865 --> 01:19:07.534
Get me out of here. Quick. start the car.

1548
01:19:12.122 --> 01:19:13.415
Yo.

1549
01:19:16.001 --> 01:19:16.835
Sup. Olivia?

1550
01:19:16.919 --> 01:19:19.129
Come on. We've got a game to win.

1551
01:19:19.213 --> 01:19:20.214
Yes!

1552
01:19:41.318 --> 01:19:43.988
This is what dreams are made of. Rusty.

1553
01:19:44.071 --> 01:19:45.823
Teams become champions.

1554
01:19:45.906 --> 01:19:47.950
Players become legends.

1555
01:19:51.078 --> 01:19:52.079
Let's go!

1556
01:19:56.875 --> 01:19:59.253
-Go. Thorns!
-This is the best day of my life.

1557
01:19:59.336 --> 01:20:00.879
I can feel myself getting invested.

1558
01:20:00.963 --> 01:20:04.174
Who cares? I'm here for it.
Break my heart. kiddo!

1559
01:20:04.258 --> 01:20:06.176
Come on. Will. Let's go!

1560
01:20:06.260 --> 01:20:07.845
Go. Thorns! Go. Thorns!

1561
01:20:07.928 --> 01:20:11.015
Tonight. Jett and Mane
will finally answer the question.

1562
01:20:11.098 --> 01:20:13.267
-who is the GOAT?
-On three.

1563
01:20:13.350 --> 01:20:15.561
-One. two. three.
-Roots run deep!

1564
01:20:16.645 --> 01:20:19.064
And here we go. Chuck.

1565
01:20:20.357 --> 01:20:21.817
Unbelievable!

1566
01:20:21.900 --> 01:20:24.236
Mane Attraction gets the tip over Lenny.

1567
01:20:28.157 --> 01:20:31.827
Mane drills one home.
sending a strong message to the Thorns.

1568
01:20:34.580 --> 01:20:36.915
You're too small.

1569
01:20:38.375 --> 01:20:39.376
Come on. Will.

1570
01:20:39.460 --> 01:20:41.545
Show 'em who's too small.

1571
01:20:46.467 --> 01:20:47.384
Eyes on me.

1572
01:20:49.261 --> 01:20:50.637
Jett with the sweet pass.

1573
01:20:51.180 --> 01:20:52.014
Thorns respond.

1574
01:20:52.097 --> 01:20:53.057
Yeah!

1575
01:20:53.807 --> 01:20:57.394
As the first quarter comes to a close.
it's still anyone's game.

1576
01:20:58.437 --> 01:21:00.272
We should be frying these fools.

1577
01:21:00.356 --> 01:21:04.360
Take 'em out if you have to.
but hold on to that lead.

1578
01:21:08.030 --> 01:21:09.073
Harris on a break!

1579
01:21:09.156 --> 01:21:10.657
Nuh-uh! Not today!

1580
01:21:10.741 --> 01:21:11.909
Will. watch out!

1581
01:21:15.245 --> 01:21:16.413
Hard hit on Jett.

1582
01:21:16.497 --> 01:21:17.831
No foul call.

1583
01:21:19.249 --> 01:21:20.292
What?

1584
01:21:24.129 --> 01:21:25.589
Oh. no.

1585
01:21:29.009 --> 01:21:31.220
This injury could take you out permanently

1586
01:21:31.303 --> 01:21:33.472
if you put any more weight on this leg.

1587
01:21:35.641 --> 01:21:36.642
I'm sorry. y'all.

1588
01:21:36.725 --> 01:21:37.976
Jett.

1589
01:21:38.519 --> 01:21:40.396
I didn't mean for you to get hurt.

1590
01:21:40.479 --> 01:21:42.314
Hey. hey. It's not your fault.

1591
01:21:43.023 --> 01:21:45.859
But I think I'm done.

1592
01:21:47.403 --> 01:21:48.404
What are we gonna do?

1593
01:21:48.487 --> 01:21:50.197
We can't win without Jett.

1594
01:21:50.280 --> 01:21:52.866
What? We're all thinking it.

1595
01:22:03.585 --> 01:22:08.632
Look. "roots run deep”.
that's more than just a cheer.

1596
01:22:09.633 --> 01:22:12.553
You guys have no idea
what you mean to this city.

1597
01:22:13.345 --> 01:22:16.557
My mom told me to dream big.

1598
01:22:17.141 --> 01:22:22.479
And for Vineland. there is no dream bigger
than bringing home a Claw.

1599
01:22:22.563 --> 01:22:25.482
This might be the last time
Vineland Thorns ever play.

1600
01:22:25.566 --> 01:22:27.359
And we ain't gonna go out like this.

1601
01:22:27.443 --> 01:22:29.570
Yeah. you heard the rook.

1602
01:22:31.405 --> 01:22:32.823
Let's dream big.

1603
01:22:42.458 --> 01:22:44.042
Is that-- Is that Jett?

1604
01:22:44.126 --> 01:22:46.170
-Did she just--
-Yeah. Jett!

1605
01:22:46.253 --> 01:22:49.256
-Jett. it's so good to see you again!
-Love you. Jett!

1606
01:22:51.717 --> 01:22:53.302
Jett. Jett.

1607
01:22:53.385 --> 01:22:56.972
Jett. Jett. Jett!

1608
01:22:57.055 --> 01:23:01.643
A well-deserved standing ovation
for the legendary Jett Fillmore.

1609
01:23:02.186 --> 01:23:03.604
Jett. Jett.

1610
01:23:03.687 --> 01:23:06.273
Jett. Jett. Jett.

1611
01:23:06.356 --> 01:23:07.608
Welcome back. GOAT.

1612
01:23:07.691 --> 01:23:10.777
Jett. Jett. Jett. Jett.

1613
01:23:12.362 --> 01:23:13.322
Archie.

1614
01:23:15.157 --> 01:23:16.909
Harris is on a tear.

1615
01:23:17.367 --> 01:23:18.994
The Thorns are all tied up.

1616
01:23:19.912 --> 01:23:21.955
-Olivia!
-1 got this.

1617
01:23:30.631 --> 01:23:32.007
I am that bird.

1618
01:23:32.090 --> 01:23:33.592
I am that bird.

1619
01:23:39.056 --> 01:23:40.807
She can fly!

1620
01:23:40.891 --> 01:23:42.851
I can fly!

1621
01:23:42.935 --> 01:23:44.728
She can fly?

1622
01:23:46.271 --> 01:23:49.900
Olivia Burke just posterized Mane!

1623
01:23:49.983 --> 01:23:51.985
I am losing my mind here!

1624
01:23:52.069 --> 01:23:53.779
Olivia!

1625
01:23:53.862 --> 01:23:55.864
-That's right.
-Go. Livvy!

1626
01:23:55.948 --> 01:23:57.908
-Go. Thorns! Go. Thorns!
-We can do it!

1627
01:23:57.991 --> 01:24:00.369
Smalls ball! Ostriches fly!

1628
01:24:00.452 --> 01:24:02.454
These are the Thorns we came to see!

1629
01:24:02.538 --> 01:24:04.665
Look who's the poster child now.

1630
01:24:08.961 --> 01:24:10.754
Time out. Magma.

1631
01:24:10.837 --> 01:24:13.632
Word of advice? Stay off social media.

1632
01:24:14.174 --> 01:24:16.301
We gotta turn this around now.

1633
01:24:16.385 --> 01:24:20.347
-Where my Maniacs at?
-Mane! Mane! Mane!

1634
01:24:20.430 --> 01:24:23.308
Uh-oh. I think we've got
some seismic activity.

1635
01:24:23.392 --> 01:24:25.227
Just listen to that crowd.

1636
01:24:25.310 --> 01:24:29.022
-They're going crazy.
-Oh. yeah!

1637
01:24:29.565 --> 01:24:31.275
Let's go!

1638
01:24:35.153 --> 01:24:36.488
Archie's trapped with no way out.

1639
01:24:36.572 --> 01:24:37.864
I know the feeling. Rusty.

1640
01:24:38.699 --> 01:24:40.367
Whoa! And up goes Lenny.

1641
01:24:43.245 --> 01:24:45.455
Jett can't save you now.

1642
01:24:48.875 --> 01:24:50.168
Hard foul by Mane.

1643
01:24:50.252 --> 01:24:51.837
-What?
-You gotta call that!

1644
01:24:51.920 --> 01:24:54.298
The zebra and the horse
are working together.

1645
01:24:54.381 --> 01:24:56.008
-Boo!
-Come on! That's a foul.

1646
01:24:58.302 --> 01:25:00.429
Really? That's how you want to win?

1647
01:25:01.013 --> 01:25:03.140
What you gonna do about it. small?

1648
01:25:03.223 --> 01:25:04.474
Hey. Mane!

1649
01:25:05.183 --> 01:25:07.436
He's not a small.

1650
01:25:07.519 --> 01:25:12.357
He's a medium!

1651
01:25:12.441 --> 01:25:13.400
Hey. break it up!

1652
01:25:14.610 --> 01:25:17.696
-Let me at him! Let me at him!
-Relax!

1653
01:25:18.614 --> 01:25:21.491
Keep your hooves off my teammates.

1654
01:25:21.575 --> 01:25:22.743
Get him. Daddy!

1655
01:25:22.826 --> 01:25:24.536
Make him bleed!

1656
01:25:24.620 --> 01:25:26.121
That's not what you want to see.

1657
01:25:26.204 --> 01:25:27.539
Speak for yourself.

1658
01:25:27.623 --> 01:25:30.083
Flagrant two. Number 34. ejected.

1659
01:25:30.167 --> 01:25:32.419
Are you kidding me? Mane started it.

1660
01:25:32.502 --> 01:25:34.087
-Where's his foul?
-Cry about it.

1661
01:25:34.171 --> 01:25:37.132
The rules state
Thorns need five players or they forfeit.

1662
01:25:37.674 --> 01:25:38.800
Hit me again.

1663
01:25:40.886 --> 01:25:42.012
Okay. okay.

1664
01:25:42.095 --> 01:25:45.098
I haven't played since
my rec league days. but I guess I could--

1665
01:25:51.813 --> 01:25:53.065
Put me in. Coach.

1666
01:25:53.565 --> 01:25:56.151
I got a game to win.

1667
01:25:58.695 --> 01:26:00.322
Jett. you can barely walk.

1668
01:26:00.405 --> 01:26:03.575
No. We can't let you do this.
You'll just make it worse.

1669
01:26:03.659 --> 01:26:04.743
You think they bought it?

1670
01:26:06.078 --> 01:26:07.079
I do.

1671
01:26:07.162 --> 01:26:10.123
I think we have about three seconds
before they catch on.

1672
01:26:10.207 --> 01:26:12.000
But that's all we need. You all ready?

1673
01:26:12.084 --> 01:26:14.002
I've been trying to run a play
like this all season.

1674
01:26:14.086 --> 01:26:16.880
but some hothead kept interrupting me.

1675
01:26:16.963 --> 01:26:18.840
That's a great play.

1676
01:26:18.924 --> 01:26:20.842
Yeah. It was worth the wait.

1677
01:26:23.804 --> 01:26:24.971
Roots run deep!

1678
01:26:25.055 --> 01:26:27.516
The Thorns are down by two
with 20 seconds on the clock.

1679
01:26:27.599 --> 01:26:29.685
Jett's gonna lay it all on the line.

1680
01:26:29.768 --> 01:26:30.894
What a competitor!

1681
01:26:30.977 --> 01:26:32.646
Listen up. Double-team her.

1682
01:26:32.729 --> 01:26:34.523
Triple-team her if you have to.

1683
01:26:34.606 --> 01:26:36.900
Do not let her out of your sight.

1684
01:26:36.983 --> 01:26:38.318
Jett's fighting an injury.

1685
01:26:38.402 --> 01:26:39.569
The court is unstable.

1686
01:26:39.653 --> 01:26:41.988
Do you still want her
taking the final shot?

1687
01:26:42.072 --> 01:26:48.912
With fire and brimstone bringing judgment
and wrath to us all. I want Fillmore!

1688
01:27:30.203 --> 01:27:31.371
Will!

1689
01:27:33.832 --> 01:27:35.709
Come on. Get past me.

1690
01:27:35.792 --> 01:27:36.960
I don't have to.

1691
01:28:10.786 --> 01:28:13.413
Our bestie just won the Claw.

1692
01:28:13.497 --> 01:28:15.624
-That's my boy!
-Hold me. Daryl.

1693
01:28:16.666 --> 01:28:19.085
For the first time in 50 years.

1694
01:28:19.169 --> 01:28:21.046
the Vineland Thorns are champions!

1695
01:28:21.129 --> 01:28:23.006
Miracles can happen. folks.

1696
01:28:23.089 --> 01:28:24.758
I love this game.

1697
01:28:24.841 --> 01:28:27.302
And I love you. Rusty.

1698
01:28:28.637 --> 01:28:31.515
I love you too. Chuckles.

1699
01:28:38.396 --> 01:28:40.357
Attaboy. Will!

1700
01:28:40.440 --> 01:28:41.441
Honey!

1701
01:28:41.525 --> 01:28:44.027
Let's have another dozen kids.

1702
01:28:46.071 --> 01:28:50.784
Ten years. ten teams. one Claw. baby!

1703
01:28:50.867 --> 01:28:53.203
We are champions!

1704
01:28:53.286 --> 01:28:54.538
-Daddy!
-Daddy!

1705
01:28:54.621 --> 01:28:55.831
You were so cool.

1706
01:28:55.914 --> 01:28:58.625
Daddy was pretty cool. right?
I was like...

1707
01:28:59.918 --> 01:29:01.211
-We love you.
-We love you.

1708
01:29:02.295 --> 01:29:03.421
I love you girls.

1709
01:29:05.131 --> 01:29:08.343
Hey. Mane. Good game. Let me help you up.

1710
01:29:10.178 --> 01:29:13.723
-Hey. your hair is on fire.
-What?

1711
01:29:13.807 --> 01:29:15.517
Oh. no. No. No.

1712
01:29:15.600 --> 01:29:16.893
Not the hair.

1713
01:29:20.105 --> 01:29:21.815
-Will!
-Jett.

1714
01:29:21.898 --> 01:29:23.608
We're champions. baby.

1715
01:29:23.692 --> 01:29:26.027
Oh. Jett! We did it! We actually did it!

1716
01:29:26.111 --> 01:29:27.612
No. you did it.

1717
01:29:27.696 --> 01:29:29.406
Looks like moms was right.

1718
01:29:33.910 --> 01:29:34.953
-Jett. you okay?
-I'm fine.

1719
01:29:35.036 --> 01:29:36.037
-You good?
-I'm fine.

1720
01:29:36.121 --> 01:29:39.624
I just can't feel my legs.
but I'm a champion. baby.

1721
01:29:40.375 --> 01:29:44.254
Never thought I'd see the day
Jett Fillmore passed the ball.

1722
01:29:44.337 --> 01:29:45.338
Security!

1723
01:29:45.422 --> 01:29:46.631
Hold up. suck a.

1724
01:29:46.715 --> 01:29:50.051
-Playtime?
-Should we destroy?

1725
01:29:50.677 --> 01:29:52.512
Destroy!

1726
01:29:52.596 --> 01:29:55.056
Do you know who I am?

1727
01:29:55.140 --> 01:29:56.516
Hey. you were right about Will.

1728
01:29:56.600 --> 01:29:58.476
He's a great addition to the team.

1729
01:29:58.560 --> 01:30:00.186
Bye. piglet.

1730
01:30:00.729 --> 01:30:06.067
Introducing your Roar champions.

1731
01:30:06.151 --> 01:30:11.281
the Vineland Thorns!

1732
01:30:14.075 --> 01:30:17.162
Yeah! Let's go. Vineland! Let's go!

1733
01:30:19.080 --> 01:30:20.165
Horns up. everybody.

1734
01:30:20.248 --> 01:30:21.875
Vineland!

1735
01:30:22.709 --> 01:30:24.628
I think it's time they hear from...

1736
01:30:27.130 --> 01:30:28.214
the GOAT.

1737
01:30:28.882 --> 01:30:31.051
Willt Will! Willt Will!

1738
01:30:31.134 --> 01:30:32.886
Willt Will! Will!

1739
01:30:32.969 --> 01:30:34.387
Medium fries did it!

1740
01:30:39.017 --> 01:30:40.560
I... I...

1741
01:30:40.644 --> 01:30:42.479
I don't even know what to say right now.

1742
01:30:42.979 --> 01:30:44.898
-This is crazy.
-We love you. Will!

1743
01:30:44.981 --> 01:30:45.982
Oh. wow.

1744
01:30:47.442 --> 01:30:48.652
I mean.

1745
01:30:49.986 --> 01:30:52.030
I saw Jett play when...

1746
01:30:52.113 --> 01:30:53.365
when I was just a kid.

1747
01:30:54.199 --> 01:30:59.913
Then I told my mom. I said.
"I'm gonna be just like her."

1748
01:31:01.706 --> 01:31:03.416
And you know what's crazy?

1749
01:31:03.917 --> 01:31:06.461
My mom actually believed it.

1750
01:31:07.087 --> 01:31:10.465
She always seemed to know
those kinds of things. you know?

1751
01:31:10.548 --> 01:31:13.176
Like she always knew

1752
01:31:13.259 --> 01:31:16.346
that even if she couldn't be here for me.

1753
01:31:16.429 --> 01:31:18.640
Vineland would be.

1754
01:31:18.723 --> 01:31:20.684
You delivered for me...

1755
01:31:20.767 --> 01:31:22.435
Will done changed the game.

1756
01:31:23.061 --> 01:31:25.438
And you always had my back...

1757
01:31:27.190 --> 01:31:29.484
and you inspired me.

1758
01:31:31.861 --> 01:31:35.907
We brought the Claw home!

1759
01:31:41.121 --> 01:31:46.209
And even if the Thorns don't have
a home in Vineland anymore...

1760
01:31:49.379 --> 01:31:53.675
no one can take this Claw away from us!

1761
01:31:56.761 --> 01:31:59.973
Vineland will be champions forever!

1762
01:32:01.975 --> 01:32:04.352
Modo has something to say!

1763
01:32:05.270 --> 01:32:09.899
Thorns staying in Vineland!

1764
01:32:11.317 --> 01:32:14.320
Modo is team owner.

1765
01:32:14.404 --> 01:32:15.655
Wait. How?

1766
01:32:20.744 --> 01:32:21.995
All in.

1767
01:32:22.078 --> 01:32:23.371
